name: Logo (White) on Black
description:
Limited Edition "OFFICIAL LOGO" TEE - White on Black Shirt

After thousands of hits to our www.IMNOTPIE.com website, we are proud to present our Official Logo Tees.

A fresh design marks the transition of IMNOTPIE from more than just a website, more than just a funny community, and more than just the NON-PIEST site out there!  The Limited Edition "OFFICIAL LOGO" TEE lets you represent one of the strongest BRANDS in Entertainment, and new colors including the limited edition white on red give you plenty of choices to add to your collection.  

Features heavy duty screen printing on luxurious high quality 100% cotton garment that will hold up to years of wear and care.

Sizes: M, L, XL, 2X, 3X
